_sText:
This is a japanese style secret clan hang out.
It is a pretty straight forward square map with places to hide and a few hidden rooms.

De_zenden

Originally created for the Zen-Den clan in 2008.

This new version created to mark the one year anniversary of the disbandment of the clan.

This is for everyone who kept asking to play the map. :P




Map Created by Justin Robert (Albertabound/Aircooled)








PS: paper walls are not hax and shooting through them is encouraged.
